{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a5f42cb83d","title":"对陈毅在党的全国代表会议上的发言稿的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"97ab72d4e5","index":0,"year":1955,"month":3,"day":23,"articleId":"a5f42cb83d"}],"tags":[{"id":"1feb996ca7","name":"陈毅","type":"人物"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji34","name":"毛泽东全集第34卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/34-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji34":{"comments":[{"id":"90180ea41d","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"a5f42cb83d","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"陈毅，当时任中共中央委员、国务院副总理。"},{"id":"9c730af367","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"a5f42cb83d","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"陈毅发言稿第21页上讲到：“反党分子高岗，是高岗、饶石反党联盟的首脑人物，他的反党罪行比饶激石更严重一些。毛泽东把这句话改为：“反党分子高岗，是高岗、饶激石反党联盟的首脑人物，他的反党罪行从某一点上看，或者可以说比饶激石更严重一些。”"},{"id":"9079b0a513","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"a5f42cb83d","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"饶激石，曾任中共中央委员、华东局第一书记、中央人民政府委员、华东行政委员会主席、中共中央组织部部长。1953年阴谋分裂党，集夺党和国家最高权力。1954年被揭露。1955年3月中国共产党全国代表会议通过决议，开除他的党籍。"},{"id":"607cc43ebc","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"a5f42cb83d","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"高岗，曾任中共中央政治局委员、东北局书记、中央人民政府副主席、东北行政委员会主席、国家计划委员会主席。1953年阴课分裂党，集夺党和国家最高权力。1954年被揭露。1955年3月中国共产党全国代表会议通过决议，开除他的党籍。"}],"contents":[{"id":"6c480b0deb","type":"title","text":"对陈毅在党的全国代表会议上的发言稿的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"a5f42cb83d"},{"id":"90180ea41d","type":"paragraph","text":"退陈毅同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"a5f42cb83d"},{"id":"9c730af367","type":"paragraph","text":"你的发言稿，看了一遍，觉得很好，可以和应该那样说，不算过火。在第廿一页上，我加了几个字问，我感觉，饶淞石的罪恶可能不比高岗小一些。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"a5f42cb83d"},{"id":"9079b0a513","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"a5f42cb83d"},{"id":"607cc43ebc","type":"paragraph","text":"三月廿三日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"a5f42cb83d"}],"page":{"id":"17ace2c0fe","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"a5f42cb83d","start":522,"end":522}}}},"__N_SSG":true}